, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190929025727/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-49805207|archive-date=September 29, 2019|}}</ref>他曾表示，他希望他的“竞选活动能够激发亚裔美国人参政。”<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://abc13.com/5526660/ |title=Andrew Yang supporters looking for momentum in Houston |last=Shay |first=Miya |date=September 10, 2019 |website=ABC13 Houston |access-date=September 12, 2019 |archive-date=2020-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200218114532/https://abc13.com/5526660/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>如果他被提名，他将成为第一个担任主要政党总统候选人的亚裔美国人，如果他当选，他将成为第一位亚裔美国总统。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://nextshark.com/andrew-yang-first-asian-president/ |title=He Could Be the First Asian President of the United States |last=Yang |first=Andrew |date=March 7, 2019 |website=NextShark | |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190427052212/https://nextshark.com/andrew-yang-first-asian-president/ |archive-date=April 27, 2019 |access-date=March 11, 2019}}</ref>

